2--controlled trigger press.

8
00:00:27,430 --> 00:00:28,340
3--follow through.

9
00:00:28,370 --> 00:00:30,270
After the shot,you come right back to the target.

10
00:00:30,300 --> 00:00:32,290
- Now what did you do wrong?
- I didn't follow through.

11
00:00:32,290 --> 00:00:34,230
Right. You came off the target to see where you hit.

12
00:00:34,260 --> 00:00:36,370
Hotch,my firearms qualification is tomorrow morning.

13
00:00:36,410 --> 00:00:39,100
I barely passed my last one.

14
00:00:40,620 --> 00:00:44,130
Front sight,trigger press...

15
00:00:45,690 --> 00:00:47,270
follow through.

16
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:50,200
You do those 3 things,you'll hit your target every time.

17
00:01:09,450 --> 00:01:11,670
I'm not fallin' for it.

18
00:01:20,060 --> 00:01:21,600
Come on,pop.

19
00:01:23,130 --> 00:01:24,790
Stop playing.

20
00:01:35,810 --> 00:01:37,300
Oh,my god.

21
