00:29:47,580 --> 00:29:50,170
Do you see him?

507
00:29:54,220 --> 00:29:56,080
Go tell gideon.

508
00:29:56,130 --> 00:29:58,280
Reid.

509
00:30:14,220 --> 00:30:17,930
Nobody moves,and nobody dies.

510
00:30:21,140 --> 00:30:23,610
Better be a head shot.

511
00:30:24,900 --> 00:30:26,110
