539
00:32:16,490 --> 00:32:17,690
Who am I?

540
00:32:17,730 --> 00:32:19,160
What's my plan?

541
00:32:19,190 --> 00:32:21,870
I know you shot 11 people in broad daylight and left us nothing,

542
00:32:21,890 --> 00:32:24,840
you executed a cop in front of the fbi and got away clean,

543
00:32:24,870 --> 00:32:28,410
and I know your plan is to go down in a hail of bullets.

544
00:32:28,450 --> 00:32:30,950
What else do you know?

545
00:32:38,130 --> 00:32:40,730
He joined the army at 18,went to ranger school,

546
00:32:40,760 --> 00:32:45,110
did 6 years before being dishonorably discharged in '95 for conduct unbecoming,

547
00:32:45,140 --> 00:32:47,720
obviously lied about it,joined the arlington P.D.

548
00:32:47,740 --> 00:32:50,110
- You were right.He was a cop.
- For 9 months.

549
00:32:50,140 --> 00:32:53,520
When they found out he lied about the discharge,they kicked him out.

550
00:32:53,550 --> 00:32:56,670
Soon thereafter,dowd got his nursing license.

551
00:32:56,690 --> 00:33:00,830
He's been bouncing from hospital to hospital ever since.

552
00:33:00,860 --> 00:33:02,910
I know you're the smartest guy in every room you've ever been in,

553
00:33:02,940 --> 00:33:04,300
and no one's ever known it.

554
00:33:04,320 --> 00:33:07,580
People feel threatened by you and try to sabotage you every chance they get.

555
00:33:07,610 --> 00:33:08,870
You're not a bad person.

556
00:33:08,900 --> 00:33:11,000
You help save all of your victims afterwards.

557
00:33:11,020 --> 00:33:12,030
First guy wasn't your fault.

558
00:33:12,070 --> 00:33:14,970
If the emts had been there on time,he would've lived.

559
00:33:14,970 --> 00:33:19,130
Took those guys 13 minutes. 13!

560
00:33:19,410 --> 00:33:21,360
You want to barricade the door.

561
00:33:21,380 --> 00:33:23,110
- What?
- Let me and the kid do it.

562
00:33:23,140 --> 00:33:26,300
Let 'em see that you've got 2 fbi agents in here doing your bidding.

563
00:33:26,330 --> 00:33:27,700
Right,let you give them a signal.

564
00:33:27,730 --> 00:33:29,150
What signal?They knew you were in here.

565
00:33:29,170 --> 00:33:32,250
They knew you were armed.What can I tell them?

566
00:33:32,970 --> 00:33:35,650
What is this,some sort of profiler trick?

567
00:33:35,680 --> 00:33:38,370
New negotiation tactic?

568
00:33:42,120 --> 00:33:44,940
I think it's a good idea.

569
00:33:46,240 --> 00:33:48,520
Why would you wanna help me?

570
00:33:48,570 --> 00:33:50,900
I don'T.

571
00:33:52,080 --> 00:33:56,800
You said they knew I was in here.

572
00:33:57,790 --> 00:33:59,710
I said they know you're in here.

573
00:33:59,750 --> 00:34:03,000
- No. That's not what you said.
- Why does it matter?

574
00:34:03,030 --> 00:34:06,120
It matters because your partner wants to help me

575
00:34:06,140 --> 00:34:08,870
even though he doesn't know it.

576
00:34:08,910 --> 00:34:10,580
Go ahead,boss man.

577
00:34:10,610 --> 00:34:11,960
Tell him why.

578
00:34:11,990 --> 00:34:17,200
If you lie or leave anything out,pop.

579
00:34:17,970 --> 00:34:20,400
They knew he was in here,they knew he was armed and dangerous,

580
00:34:20,430 --> 00:34:22,950
and they knew that he was gonna fight till the last round,

581
00:34:22,980 --> 00:34:24,840
and they sent me in here with an unarmed kid

582
00:34:24,880 --> 00:34:28,590
who can't shoot his way out of a wet paper bag.

583
00:34:29,050 --> 00:34:30,690
They set you up.

584
00:34:30,720 --> 00:34:33,520
Exactly,and they're probably laughing about it right now.

585
00:34:33,560 --> 00:34:36,170
That's why you wanna help me.

586
00:34:36,190 --> 00:34:37,480
I wouldn't say I want to help you,

587
00:34:37,500 --> 00:34:39,950
but when they come in here to get revenge for the cop you killed,

588
00:34:39,980 --> 00:34:41,080
you're gonna go down fighting,

589
00:34:41,100 --> 00:34:44,370
and in the crossfire,a lot of us are gonna die.

590
00:34:44,420 --> 00:34:48,830
They sent me in here.I figure why make it easy for them.

591
00:34:51,290 --> 00:34:53,760
Can I talk to you for a minute?

592
00:35:02,240 --> 00:35:04,020
Please don't send your men in yet.

593
00:35:04,050 --> 00:35:08,200
You have to consider the possibility that your men are dead or at least disarmed.

594
00:35:08,230 --> 00:35:11,200
Agent hotch is a very experienced profiler.

595
00:35:11,460 --> 00:35:16,490
He's gonna do whatever he has to to get dowd to like,trust us.

596
00:35:16,520 --> 00:35:18,780
And once he does...

597
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:20,640
he'll get dowd to end this peacefully.

598
00:35:20,670 --> 00:35:24,090
I--I just...ask that you give him time.

599
00:35:24,130 --> 00:35:25,810
Dowd's already shot 10 people.

600
00:35:25,840 --> 00:35:27,710
He killed a cop.

601
00:35:27,740 --> 00:35:28,930
The cop is dead.

602
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:32,190
This man is a violent,deranged paranoid.

603
00:35:32,230 --> 00:35:34,270
It's a game.

604
00:35:34,500 --> 00:35:36,510
He's gonna--he's gonna do whatever he has to.

605
00:35:36,550 --> 00:35:37,120
You send in your men,

606
00:35:37,150 --> 00:35:41,420
they're just gonna become villains in his little hero fantasy.

607
00:35:41,610 --> 00:35:43,470
You're lettin' him call all the shots.

608
00:35:43,500 --> 00:35:45,260
How are your unarmed men gonna stop him?

609
00:35:45,290 --> 00:35:49,190
They're not unarmed.They have his profile.

610
00:35:49,420 --> 00:35:52,380
They understand him.

611
00:35:54,580 --> 00:35:57,610
3 minutes. Then my men are ready to take the E.R.

612
00:35:57,650 --> 00:36:01,180
Your men...have 3 minutes.

613
00:36:05,780 --> 00:36:09,230
You know why they took away boy genius's gun?

614
00:36:09,260 --> 00:36:10,050
Why?

615
00:36:10,100 --> 00:36:12,040
He failed his qualification.

616
00:36:12,080 --> 00:36:14,700
Twice I year,I gotta listen to him whine about requalifying.

617
00:36:14,740 --> 00:36:16,770
So I tutor him...

618
00:36:16,820 --> 00:36:18,460
and he fails again.

619
00:36:18,500 --> 00:36:20,230
You think you got it rough?

620
00:36:20,260 --> 00:36:23,220
These people done nothing but undermine me since I got here.

621
00:36:23,260 --> 00:36:25,680
Put him next to the barricade.

622
00:36:25,720 --> 00:36:28,130
That way,when they blast their way in here,both of our problems are solved.

623
00:36:28,160 --> 00:36:31,390
That sort of thing can ruin a cop's career.

624
00:36:31,430 --> 00:36:33,190
You are one sick dude.

625
00:36:33,220 --> 00:36:36,400
How do you think I found you?

626
00:36:40,720 --> 00:36:41,690
Time's up.

627
00:36:41,720 --> 00:36:43,970
Ready teams for assault.

628
00:37:05,720 --> 00:37:08,270
- Can I ask you a favor?
- You can ask.

629
00:37:08,310 --> 00:37:11,150
I figure the chances of my getting out of here alive are pretty slim.

630
00:37:11,170 --> 00:37:12,660
So?

631
00:37:12,700 --> 00:37:15,130
I want to kick the snot out of this kid.

632
00:37:15,170 --> 00:37:19,990
He's made my life miserable for 3 lousy years.

633
00:37:24,020 --> 00:37:26,330
Go ahead.Knock yourself out.

634
00:37:34,290 --> 00:37:36,720
How smart are you now,smart guy?!

635
00:37:36,750 --> 00:37:40,960
It's front sight,trigger press,follow through!

636
00:37:40,990 --> 00:37:41,910
That's enough!

637
00:37:41,950 --> 00:37:43,300
It's not that hard!

638
00:37:43,330 --> 00:37:46,240
A dalmatian could do it!

639
00:37:46,390 --> 00:37:49,600
Let go!Let go!

640
00:38:03,890 --> 00:38:05,240
Feel better?

641
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:08,170
I think he got a messege

642
00:38:13,030 --> 00:38:13,730
What's that?

643
00:38:13,780 --> 00:38:15,330
We go in 5...

644
00:38:15,380 --> 00:38:16,960
4...

645
00:38:20,250 --> 00:38:22,020
we go now!

646
00:38:22,570 --> 00:38:24,150
Hold your fire!

647
00:38:24,190 --> 00:38:26,170
Hold your fire!

648
00:38:26,480 --> 00:38:28,260
It's all clear.

649
00:38:33,050 --> 00:38:34,560
Shakespeare wrote,

650
00:38:34,590 --> 00:38:39,880
"nothing is so common as the wish to be remarkable."

651
00:38:48,370 --> 00:38:50,070
You all right?

652
00:38:52,020 --> 00:38:54,110
Nice shot.

653
00:38:54,380 --> 00:38:57,130
